{"word":"G2044 - ἐρεύγομαι - ereúgomai - er-yoog'-om-ahee - Utter","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐρεύγομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ereúgomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">er-yoog'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Utter</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to spit or spue out"},{"paragraph":"2. to be emptied, discharge itself,"},{"paragraph":"3. to pour forth words, to speak out, utter"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of uncertain affinity; to <i>belch</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>speak out:</i> - utter.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}